name: Mutton Akhni
description: A South Asian mixed rice dish with spices, meat, and/or vegetables
recipe: Boil the rice, sauté the meat/vegetables with spices, layer the rice and meat/vegetables in a pot, and cook on low heat until the rice is fully cooked

name: Fish Sushi
description: A Japanese dish of vinegar rice topped with seafood or vegetables
recipe: Cook the sushi rice, roll the rice and seafood/vegetables in Nori seaweed, and slice into bite-sized pieces

name: Lasagna
description: An Italian dish of layered pasta, meat, cheese, and tomato sauce
